  "text": "From the SEER database, patients with a diagnosis of adenocarcinoma of the prostate (International Classification of diseases-O-3 code: C61.9) between 2010 and 2016 were selected. The TNM stages were assessed by the 7th edition of American Joint Committee on Cancer [AJCC] Cancer Staging Manual [CITATION_1] . Inclusion and exclusion criteria were shown in the flowchart in detail ( Fig. 1 ). All the included patients were randomly divided into the training cohort and validation cohort with a ratio of 7:3.",
